  <h2>HOMELAB</h2>
  <p>
    Runs a mini PC hypervisor with <strong>XCP-ng</strong>, hosting several virtual machines:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Ubuntu Dev VM</strong> – for Python, automation scripts, and local development</li>
    <li><strong>Rocky Linux VM</strong> – for Red Hat ecosystem testing</li>
    <li><strong>Kali Linux VM</strong> – for ethical hacking and security testing</li>
    <li><strong>Prod Debian VM</strong> – hosts Nginx-powered personal site, SMB, and FTP servers (soon to be SFTP)</li>
    <li><strong>XOA VM</strong> – running Xen Orchestra for managing XCP-ng infrastructure via web UI</li>
  </ul>

