  <h2>EXAMPLES</h2>
  <pre><code># create a virtual environment
python3 -m venv env

# run script to sync files
bash sync.sh

# start SMB and FTP services
sudo systemctl start smbd vsftpd

# test VLAN isolation from Pi
ping -c 3 192.168.99.10

# pull latest site update
cd /var/www/info && git pull origin main

# monitor VMs using XO CLI
yarn xo-cli list-vms</code></pre>

